outputs.output_descr: Montenegro is one of over 60 countries that are facilitating national discussions on the post 2015 development agenda.  The output from these consultations will feed into the global United Nations Development Group Report that will be the basis for the inter-governmental consultative process on post 2015 agenda; Post 2015 High Level Panel Report; and the United Nations Secretary General report to the UN General Assembly in September 2013. Equally important for Montenegro, the input from the consultations will feed into the revision of the National Strategy for Sustainable Development.
donor_name: Ministry of Foreign Affairs and Trade of the Republic of korea
